      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.archetypes.37tJXZ0coihNI3BI]{Star Knight}</p>\n<p>A Hellknight of the Order of the Scourge can choose the zone of truth alternate class feature. As a standard action, you can cast @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.spells.V3mnCtb962WQlICq]{Zone Of Truth} as a spell-like ability. You can use this ability once per day, plus one additional time per day at 10th level and every 4 levels thereafter. The save DC is equal to 12 + your key ability score modifier.</p>"
